# Paper / manuscript source — kept locally; arXiv hosts the canonical PDF.
# The figure-generation script and the produced figures ARE tracked, because
# the paper explicitly advertises "We release code and figure-generation
# scripts to support full reproduction" (see README -> Reproducing the paper).
arxiv_template.tex
references.bib
PAPER_DRAFT.md
ABSTRACT.md
RELATED_WORK.md
TOPIC_DECISION.md
# media/ figures and scripts/paper_figures.py are intentionally tracked.

# Local-only artifacts (raw result archives, paper drafts, sample PDFs, CV).
# None of these belong in the public repo; the canonical paper is on arXiv
# and the canonical results live under results/raw/ as JSONL.
*.zip
Sample_paper*.pdf
resume.pdf
Fianl submission draft/
PREPRINT FINAL VERSION/

